Sentencas: In this paper we investigate the oscillatory response of a methane fuelled solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) under weakly humidified conditions.
Titulo: Current Oscillations in Solid Oxide Fuel Cells under Weakly Humidified Conditions

Sentencas: We present experimental results conducted using operating conditions which allow for direct comparison with the mathematical model presented in Sands et al. 2014.
Titulo: Current Oscillations in Solid Oxide Fuel Cells under Weakly Humidified Conditions

Sentencas: We find transitions from a stable, steady current producing state, to nonlinear autonomous oscillations, to a zero current output state, which corresponds to the pattern of behavior also observed in the model.
Titulo: Current Oscillations in Solid Oxide Fuel Cells under Weakly Humidified Conditions

Sentencas: In this paper we briefly summarize the model from Sands et al. 2014, followed by a description of the cell assembly and experimental procedures.
Titulo: Current Oscillations in Solid Oxide Fuel Cells under Weakly Humidified Conditions

Sentencas: The results are then presented, followed by a discussion and comparison with the model.
